ON THE CUSP 🤎📈

My debut EP is OUT NOWWWW!!!

I really hope y'all get into every song and connect to it. I wrote all of these from the heart. Whether it's a rowdy reminder of who you are 💪🏼or a reflective mirror of life's challenges 🥹 these tracks are reflective of the human experience.

I've never fit into a box. I'm always on the cusp of multiple things, and I'm sure many of you are the same. To all my cuspers, this EP is for you! ❤️‍🔥

June 21st - A Birthday 🎂 and Solstice ☀️ 

sol·stice

the time or date at which the sun reaches its maximum declination, marked by the longest day.

I'm grateful to still be here, y'all! Life is so exquisitely layered with people and experiences. Thank you to all of you who have poured into me, laughed with me, loved on me, uplifted me, believed in me, supported me, encouraged me, motivated me, and who continue to grow with me. I only hope that, like the Solstice I was born on, I make y'all feel like the sun is shining on you everyday day (on the longest day)!

It's my birthdayyyyyy...
More life. We up! ♥️
